    <bioghist>University of Michigan Administrator who spent time as a professor of Botany, the dean of the Rackham Graduate School, the acting dean of the College of Literature, Science, and the Arts, and interim Vice President for Academic Affairs.</bioghist>
    <scopecontent>Photographic slides taken mainly at the University of Michigan of noteworthy bumper stickers, graffiti, kiosk announcements, wall posters, and diag banners; as well as slides relating to Sussman's botany studies. Photographs of the University of Michigan's sister school in China, Chosun University. Also contains newspaper clippings, correspondnce, and reports regarding Sussman's involvement with the Rackham Graduate School and the College of Literature, Science, and the Arts.</scopecontent>
